observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Accountant shall:

Ensure that all recorded accounts payable represent goods and services actually received as at year-end to reflect the correct obligations of the LGU and not to purely rely on the recorded obligations of the MBO without careful scrutiny as to whether or not the items reflected therein qualify to be recorded as A/P;  

Make necessary correcting entries to rectify the overstatement made on the accounts payable account for a fair presentation of the F/S of the current year.

We recommend that the Local Chief Executive require the GAD Focal
Person to plan, focus and undertake definite activities which will:
a. Enhance women’s access to all types of health care;
b. Lower maternal mortality rates and provide adequate family planning
services;
c. Enhance the situation of women in the informal economy;
d. Encourage women victims of violence to report their ordeal.
